overview: Sturm last fought in March 2022, when he lost an IBO Inter-Continental super middleweight title fight to Istvan Szili.  Altay's last action was to win a split-decision win over Aleksandar Kuvac in September. The fight will take place 2/18/23 at the Porsche Zentrum in Stuttgart, Baden-Wurttemberg.
title: Felix Sturm vs Sukru Altay
